module.exports = ({
  compose: require('ramda').compose,
  fromPairs: require('ramda').fromPairs,
  map: require('ramda').map,
  mergeAll: require('ramda').mergeAll,
  pick: require('ramda').pick,
  propOr: require('ramda').propOr,
  toPairs: require('ramda').toPairs,
  type: require('ramda').type,
  values: require('ramda').values,
  find: require('ramda').find,
  is: require('ramda').is,
  anyPass: require('ramda').anyPass,
  keys: require('ramda').keys,
  flatten: require('ramda').flatten,
  pair: require('ramda').pair,
  curry: require('ramda').curry,
  assoc: require('ramda').assoc
})
